=Description=

"Earthworks stands for clean water, healthy communities and corporate accountability. The
organization works with communities and grassroots groups to reform government policies, improve
corporate practices, influence investment decisions and encourage responsible materials sourcing and
consumption. They expose the health, environmental, economic, social and cultural impacts of mining
and energy extraction through work informe by sound science."


